rolled in and thunder rumbled in the distance.<br>
Solari slowly sat up, looking down at her wounds once more before moving to clean them and bandage the once more. She stood slowly, grabbing clean clothes and putting them on. The rain started coming down, slow at first in big drops, but then falling heavier and heavier. She watched as her fellow amazons made their way quickly to shelters, whistling, she called for Alysia to join her. <br>
 &quot;I would like to know how many eyes you have out there and where they are located.&quot; She said softly over the rumble of thunder.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=daughterofshylock>Daughter of Shylock</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.picturesof.net/_wallpaper/rose_Dsc08151_WP.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Silver Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 277<br> <font color=#993300>(4/11/03 9:32 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm66.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic&index=142>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.picturesof.net/_wallpaper/rose_Dsc08151_WP.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The Planning Begins</span><hr size=1> Alysia stood forth and walked towards Solari.<br>
