<br>
Alysia ran through the forests as quick as she could, soon joining the side of Arixa and Aeceus. She blinked her blue eyes as she and the others looked down on the Roman village and tried to overhear anything being said about Hippolyte's whereabouts. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center">~*~ Jessica ~*~<br>
