 &quot;Marpe, would you like anything to eat or drink?&quot; Solari asked softly moving to get her bag. The pain in her body was subsiding and healing pain set in. Her wounds being burned to stop the bleeding and carefully wrapped. She didnt like giving into her pain, knowing that ther was still much work that needed to be done. Reaching into her bag, she grabbed a small vile and a pouch, full of herbs for tea mixtures. <br>
 &quot;I plan on in the dead of night tommorow eve to attack the village.&quot; She replied as she mixed some tea leaves in some water to be seeped over the fire. &quot; The one that took Hippolyte, I will deal with personally. I want you and Elektra to take Hippolyte to safety once we find where she is located.&quot; She looked to Marpe and smiled. &quot;Will you be ok to work with Elektra on this matter?&quot;  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=hippolyte>Hippolyte</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Golden Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 841<br> <font color=#993300>(4/17/03 7:48 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm66.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic&index=152>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.themiscrya.i-p.com/Hippwknife1ezboard.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> In the middle hut </span><hr size=1> Hippolyte slowely woke up to sounds inside the hut.  Finding herself still tied to the middle post in the room, she looked around.  Finding one of her eyes hurt and swollen, it was hard to see thru it.  There were a few men whispering to each other in the corner.  One she recognized as her captor.  She quietly wiggled her hands and felt her restraints were still tight.  <br>
<br>
Her movements must have got his attention, &quot;Awake again, slave?&quot; he laughed at her.  <br>
<br>
Hippolyte narrowed her eyes and spoke nothing.  The man stood up again and walked over to her with a wicked grin.  Grasping her neck as he stood before her.  &quot;I bet you would take a good price, slave.  But, I think I should enjoy you as a wife first.&quot;<br>
<br>
The words sent chills thru her spine.  Surely, he did not mean what he said.  Glancing over to his men, he waved them to leave.  Hippolyte for the first time, felt fear.  Slowely, he turned his head back to his captive.  &quot;I bet you have never felt a man before have you?&quot; <p>@xxx}}::::::::::::::::::::>

"We ride tonight!  With the strength that Hera has given
us-- and the strength that we have _earned_ for ourselves!  Take
what you need, but be quick.  Stay only until the sound of horn.
The moment you hear it-- we ride away.  Now-- to your horses."</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=marpeamzn>Marpe Amzn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 79<br> <font color=#993300>(4/17/03 7:55 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm66.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic&index=153>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.themiscrya.i-p.com/MarpeAmznrpg.bmp WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> plans</span><hr size=1> Marpe nodded listening to Solari.  &quot;No, my Vasilissa.  I am not hungry.  I want to go into this battle tonight cleansed.&quot;  She looked over at Elektra.  &quot;I can work with her...and she probably will with me as well.  Just will be a work relationship..not friendly.&quot;<br>
