hers.  It was obvious that none of them could see her.  Elektra turned her eyes back to look to the Goddess.  &quot;Yes, my Goddess, I want to return Hippolyte.  I am tired of waiting.  Tell me what I should do!&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=queenhera>Queen Hera</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 231<br> <font color=#993300>(4/17/03 8:08 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm66.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic&index=156>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.themiscrya.i-p.com/lilhera.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: the vision</span><hr size=1> &quot;Sacrifice, Elektra.  You must sacrifice a stallion.  Take it's life for Hippolyte.  And it must be a milkly white stallion, like the one that appeared before the birth of Hippolyte.  Offer it to the Gods of Olympus.  That we shall grant you this victory.&quot;  Hera ordered.  She remembered the day she gave the vision to Otere and the amazons.  This sacrifice had to be done. <p>~~<<<<<<{{{{@</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=elektraamazon>Elektra Amazon</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 28<br> <font color=#993300>(4/17/03 8:25 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm66.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic&index=157>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/ddelektradd/images